N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 8.14 - Removal of grade markings

State Regulations

The commissioner or his representative may inspect cheese
for compliance with the quality standards and when there is evidence that the
grade markings have been placed upon cheese which does not meet the minimum
quality standards, may order the removal or obliteration of such grade
markings. Notes
